name: Brits out for the lads
description: This is my first attempt at creating a Checkpoint from scratch (albeit trained against Stable Diffusion 1.5). I wanted to create a model that would re-create the British style of "Reader's Wives" amature glamour modelling of the 80's and 90's, in magazines like Razzle and Escort. It does't require any keywords as such, but "large breasts" and "Natural Pubic Hair" will pull out of the LoRA's I trained and one or two others from the community. Feedback appreciated.
